            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EAmos%207%3A1-9%3A15%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22amos_7_1%22%20bk%3D%22amos%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EAmos%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Vision%20of%20Locusts%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20showed%20me%20a%20vision.%20I%20saw%20him%20preparing%20to%20send%20a%20vast%20swarm%20of%20locusts%20over%20the%20land.%20This%20was%20after%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20share%20had%20been%20harvested%20from%20the%20fields%20and%20as%20the%20main%20crop%20was%20coming%20up.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22amos_7_2%22%20bk%3D%22amos%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20my%20vision%20the%20locusts%20ate%20every%20green%20plant%20in%20sight.%20Then%20I%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3BSovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20please%20forgive%20us%20or%20we%20will%20not%20survive%2C%20for%20Israel%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EJacob%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%207%3A5.%20See%20note%20on%203%3A13.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20so%20small.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22amos_7_3%22%20bk%3D%22amos%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20relented%20from%20this%20plan.%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20not%20do%20it%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22amos_7_4%22%20bk%3D%22amos%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Vision%20of%20Fire%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20showed%20me%20another%20vision.%20I%20saw%20him%20preparing%20to%20punish%20his%20people%20with%20a%20great%20fire.%20The%20fire%20had%20burned%20up%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20sea%20and%20was%20devouring%20the%20entire%20land.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22amos_7_5%22%20bk%3D%22amos%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20I%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3BSovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20please%20stop%20or%20we%20will%20not%20survive%2C%20for%20Israel%20is%20so%20small.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22amos_7_6%22%20bk%3D%22amos%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20relented%20from%20this%20plan%2C%20too.%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20not%20do%20that%20either%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20said%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22amos_7_7%22%20bk%3D%22amos%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Vision%20of%20a%20Plumb%20Line%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20showed%20me%20another%20vision.%20I%20saw%20the%20Lord%20standing%20beside%20a%20wall%20that%20had%20been%20built%20using%20a%20plumb%20line.%20He%20was%20using%20a%20plumb%20line%20to%20see%20if%20it%20was%20still%20straight.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22amos_7_8%22%20bk%3D%22amos%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BAmos%2C%20what%20do%20you%20see%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EI%20answered%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BA%20plumb%20line.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EAnd%20the%20Lord%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20test%20my%20people%20with%20this%20plumb%20line.%20I%20will%20no%20longer%20ignore%20all%20their%20sins.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22amos_7_9%22%20bk%3D%22amos%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20pagan%20shrines%20of%20your%20ancestors%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eof%20Isaac.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20will%20be%20ruined%2C%20and%20the%20temples%20of%20Israel%20will%20be%20destroyed%3B%20I%20will%20bring%20the%20dynasty%20of%20King%20Jeroboam%20to%20a%20sudden%20end.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22amos_7_10%22%20bk%3D%22amos%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EAmos%20and%20Amaziah%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Amaziah%2C%20the%20priest%20of%20Bethel%2C%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20Jeroboam%2C%20king%20of%20Israel%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BAmos%20is%20hatching%20a%20plot%20against%20you%20right%20here%20on%20your%20very%20doorstep!%20What%20he%20is%20saying%20is%20intolerable.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22amos_7_11%22%20bk%3D%22amos%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20is%20saying%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BJeroboam%20will%20soon%20be%20killed%2C%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20will%20be%20sent%20away%20into%20exile.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22amos